@node "shareware" "Vokabi 2 guide - Shareware"
@next "license"
@prev "todo"
Vokabi 2 is shareware. The unregistered version has the following
restrictions:

  - You can't save the configuration.

  - You can't feed more than 50 words


If you want to use these possibilities (or if you want to give some reward to
me for my effort) should print a registration form, occupy it, add a cheque
for

  DM   25,-  or
  US-$ 17,-

and send it to me. You'll get the freshest version and a personalized keyfile
which abolishes the restrictions.
@endnode

